extends layouts/landing

block content
	#container
		header.wrapper
			#header_container.center
				a(href='/')
					img#logo(alt="modivle logo",src='/img/logo/modivleblack.png')
				if !loggedin
					span#login

		#main.wrapper
			.center.content
				h1 Privacy Policy

				h2 General Information
				p We collect the names, e-mail addresses, and username of those who use the application.

				p We use Google Analytics and Mixpanel to track page views and usage of various features within the application.

				p The information collected is used to improve the application in terms of which features are further developed or removed.

				p The information will not shared with or sold to other organisations for commercial purposes.

				h2 Information Gathering and Usage
				p When you authenticate IVLE, we request for your name, email address and username in order to keep track of the number of unique students that have accessed used the application.

				p This collected information is used solely for the following purposes:

				ul 
					li To personalise your experience (your information helps us to better respond to your individual needs)
				
					li Measuring the growth of the application
				
					li Improving the application through analysis of user actions and resulting retention rates.
				
					li To send periodic emails.
				
				h2 Cookies
				p A cookie is a small amount of data, which often includes an anonymous unique identifier, that is sent to your browser from a web site's computers and stored on your computer's hard drive.

				p Cookies are required to use MODIVLE.

				p We use cookies to record current session information, but do not use permanent cookies. You are required to re-authenticate to IVLE after a certain period of time has elapsed.

				h2 Changes
				p MODIVLE may periodically update this policy. We will notify you about significant changes in the way we treat personal information by sending a notice to your email address or by placing a prominent notice on our site.

				h2 Questions
				p Any questions about this Privacy Policy should be addressed to <a href='mailto:modivle@yrmichael.com?subject=MODIVLE Privacy Policy Enquiry'>modivle@yrmichael.com</a>.
		.push


	footer.wrapper
		#footer_container.center
			//- a(href='').footer_link Release Notes
